    "description": "Daisan Co., Ltd. plans, designs, manufactures, and sells construction hardware, temporary equipment and other related services in Japan. It also manufactures general temporary construction materials used in mid- to high-rise building construction and bridge construction. In addition, its overseas business mainly provides ancillary construction work, such as thermal insulation work, scaffolding work, electrical work, and offers related construction and personnel dispatch services. Further, the company offers single pipe joint with visible lock, retractable pedals, HAP security system, simple morning glory, curing material for opening, DL and BL guard, DS coupler, DS bracket, DS step, DS hanger stage, bike and bamboo scaffoldings, and le-volt. Daisan Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1975 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
